body:
I have come across many discussions lately on the board, talking about their teams being bad. It got me thinking, &quot;what is peoples opinion on a deserved win or loss?&quot;
Cause to me, I see some games, where I think, they hard carried but their team holds them back. I have run into this too, where I think I deserve to win because I did much better than my team. I&#039;m in B1, so I&#039;m not too surprised that most of my teams are garbage. (Honestly, I want a pro player to judge that.)

But what factors lead to a deserved win or loss?
